I am a spider.

262
00:21:02,614 --> 00:21:03,887
Welcome...

263
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,893
to my web.

264
00:21:14,247 --> 00:21:17,407
I'll get you to a hospital.
You will make it. Believe me.

265
00:21:17,434 --> 00:21:19,053
I don't know what to believe.

266
00:21:21,107 --> 00:21:23,107
I don't know what's real anymore.

267
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:26,473
This is real. My love
for you. That's real.

268
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,367
You might be... the only one...

269
00:21:29,807 --> 00:21:31,060
who truly loves me.

270
00:21:31,660 --> 00:21:34,860
Be glad that someone
loves you, Barteljaap.

271
00:21:36,134 --> 00:21:37,007
Brinte...

272
00:21:38,407 --> 00:21:39,473
I love...

273
00:21:47,540 --> 00:21:48,427
No.

274
00:21:59,487 --> 00:22:00,733
Are you the translator?

275
00:22:03,867 --> 00:22:05,867
Could you tell me what you saw?

276
00:22:06,414 --> 00:22:07,920
I invoke my <i>G-code</i>.

277
00:22:08,480 --> 00:22:09,840
I don't talk to pigs.

278
00:22:10,180 --> 00:22:11,547
I'm no snitch, nigga.

279
00:22:17,120 --> 00:22:17,980
Done.

